    <item>
      <title>索马里热门海滩酒店发生自杀式爆炸，造成 37 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/suicide-bombing-in-somalia-kills-32-at-popular-beach-hotel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五晚，索马里首都摩加迪沙一家热门海滨酒店发生自杀式炸弹爆炸，造成至少 37 人死亡，数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/suicide-bombing-in-somalia-kills-32-at-popular-beach-hotel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 11:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称击沉了俄罗斯黑海潜艇并袭击了空军基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/war-in-ukraine-drones-hit-russian-airfield-and-fuel-depots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军队称，他们在对俄罗斯多个地区发动的大规模无人机袭击中袭击了一座军用机场，并声称周五的袭击击沉了克里米亚的一艘黑海舰队潜艇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/war-in-ukraine-drones-hit-russian-airfield-and-fuel-depots</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 10:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
